Temptation
├── constructor
│   ├── it should set REGISTRY to the provided address
│   ├── it should set TOKEN to the provided address
│   └── it should set owner to msg.sender
├── deposit(uint256 amount)
│   ├── it should transfer tokens from caller to temptation
│   ├── it should emit Deposited event
│   └── given multiple deposits
│       └── it should accumulate the total balance
├── withdraw
│   ├── when caller has no permission token
│   │   └── it should revert with NoPermissionToken
│   ├── when token metadata temptation does not match this temptation
│   │   └── it should revert with InvalidTemptation
│   ├── when amount exceeds permitted max
│   │   └── it should revert with ExceedsPermittedAmount
│   ├── when temptation has insufficient token balance
│   │   └── it should revert with InsufficientBalance
│   └── when all checks pass
│       ├── it should transfer tokens to the caller
│       ├── it should reduce the temptation token balance
│       ├── it should emit Withdrawn event
│       └── given amount equals maxAmount
│           └── it should succeed
└── balance
    ├── when temptation is empty
    │   └── it should return 0
    └── when temptation has tokens
        └── it should return the temptation's token balance
